**Title:** Whispering Tides and Moonlit Dreams

**Description:** Immerse yourself in the tranquil tale of Oliver, an introspective 11-year-old who finds solace and wonder along the serene coastal dunes. With his loyal otter companion, Mira, by his side, Oliver embarks on an evocative journey under the moonlit sky. As they explore new paths and face gentle challenges, Oliver discovers the beauty of connection and the power of empathy. This soothing sleep story, crafted to ease anxiety and nurture emotional calm, offers a gentle rhythm to lull you into restful slumber. Let the calming narrative and serene soundscape guide you toward a peaceful night's sleep.

